Package es.uam.eps.ir.relison.sna.metrics.pair

Class ExpandedNeighborCountedOverlap<U>

java.lang.Object
es.uam.eps.ir.relison.sna.metrics.pair.ExpandedNeighborCountedOverlap<U>
Type Parameters:
U - Type of the users.
All Implemented Interfaces:
PairMetric<U>
public class ExpandedNeighborCountedOverlap<U>
extends java.lang.Object
implements PairMetric<U>
Expanded neighbor overlap. Finds the size of the intersection between users at distance at most 2 of one user, with the neighborhood of another. Users' weight depend on the number of times they appear.
Author:
Javier Sanz-Cruzado (javier.sanz-cruzado@uam.es), Pablo Castells (pablo.castells@uam.es)
